x4freetext: The data of LiF target with 15 and 30 degrees were
taken from this reference.
Beam intensity is 1 nA.
- Chemical-form of target is element.
- Physical-form of target is solid.
- Target-thickness: 2mm for C, 1mm for LiF and Si,
0.5mm for the others
EJ-301 liquid organic scintillator
the geometry of the detector
the response functions of the detector
the scattering of neutrons in a thick target
and the air
contributions of the other sources (about 1%)
S.Shin
